  "description": {
    "zh": "想象一下，过去有多少人经常在Ultra闲逛，带着孩子的妈妈，相亲相爱的夫妇，等等。那时候每个商店都是顾客盈门，该死，感觉真酷，或许你还记得曾经的美好回忆。我离题太远了，长话短说，让我们把活儿赶快搞定吧。帮这个世界一个忙，把Ultra里面的Scav清理干净，那样我才能派我的小弟们进去。我早就警告过他们如果不离开会怎样的。",
    "en": "Just imagine how many folks used to hang around at Ultra, mommies with kids, couples, and so on, everybody stocked tight, too. Damn, felt so cool, a lot of movement went down, you probably remember if you're from here. But I digress into nostalgia, no time for that, let’s get shit done, yo. These days Ultra is filled with Scavs, stealing whatever they want, you know. Do the world a favor, clean Ultra up from those shitheads, so I could send my boys in. Gonna have a gift for you if you're down for the task."
  },
